                            <comment id="14679425" author="hadoopqa" created="Mon, 10 Aug 2015 00:19:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;red&quot;&gt;-1 overall&lt;/font&gt;.  Here are the results of testing the latest attachment &lt;br/&gt;
